# Task 4 - Styling and Responsive Design

## Overview

This project was developed as part of the ApexPlanet Web Development Internship. The objective of this task was to improve the user interface and user experience by applying custom styling and making the application responsive across different devices.

## Features Implemented

### User Interface Enhancements

* Modern gradient background
* Responsive card layouts
* Professional button styling
* Improved form design
* Consistent color scheme
* Bootstrap Icons integration

### Responsive Design

* Mobile-friendly layout
* Responsive forms
* Responsive dashboard
* Responsive user management table
* Device compatibility testing

### Styling Improvements

* Custom CSS styling
* Card shadows and rounded corners
* Hover effects on buttons
* Improved spacing and alignment
* Better typography

